<s> In an attempt to unify the responses from MERGE and UPDATE, and to address the concerns some have expressed for parsing the responses of these methods, I propose that: (a) the DAV:ignore-set is dropped from the responses.  </s>
<s> What would you do with them anyway?  </s>
<s> Speak up if you have a use-case that requires these; and, (b) the response marshalling should be in the Multi-Status format so that implementations can reuse their existing code.  </s>
<s> I think the responses will fit well in this format.  </s>
<s> Note that (a) will simplify the protocol, and (b) will simplify the implementation without changing the semantics of the operations.  </s>
<s> They are relatively minor changes.  </s>
<s> Regards, Tim  </s>
